---
// Pricing/Engagement Section
// How We Work
---

<section class="pricing section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="big-bold-text">START YOUR APP'S DAY-1 WITH US.</h2>

    <p class="intro-text">
      Two meetings. One clear path forward.
    </p>

    <div class="engagement-steps">
      <!-- Meeting 1 -->
      <div class="engagement-step">
        <span class="step-badge">Meeting 1</span>
        <h3 class="step-title">Free Brief (Your Story)</h3>
        <p class="step-description">
          Tell us about your business, your challenge, your vision. We listen, we ask questions, we start understanding your patterns.
        </p>
        <ul class="step-details">
          <li>No cost, no commitment</li>
          <li>NDA available if needed</li>
          <li>60-90 minutes of focused discussion</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Meeting 2 -->
      <div class="engagement-step">
        <span class="step-badge">Meeting 2</span>
        <h3 class="step-title">The Proposal (Our Plan)</h3>
        <p class="step-description">
          We present a complete working plan—from foundation discovery through your final BRS. You'll see exactly how we'll uncover what you need.
        </p>
        <ul class="step-details">
          <li>Detailed discovery roadmap</li>
          <li>Timeline and process breakdown</li>
          <li>PoC plan customized for your project</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="work-details">
      <div class="detail-card">
        <h4>The Work</h4>
        <p>
          Time-based contract. Typically 5-7 PoCs to reach solid requirements. Duration depends on your product's complexity and discovery needs.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="detail-card highlight">
        <h4>The Outcome</h4>
        <p>
          A Business Requirements Specification that doesn't just describe features—it explains why they matter and how they serve your strategy. This BRS becomes your development team's north star.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .pricing {
    background-color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .pricing .big-bold-text {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .intro-text {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-4xl);
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .engagement-steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(380px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-3xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4xl);
    max-width: 900px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .engagement-step {
    background-color: var(--color-base);
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-border);
    transition: border-color var(--transition-base), transform var(--transition-base);
  }

  .engagement-step:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent-cool);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .step-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: var(--color-accent-warm);
    color: var(--color-white);
    padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-md);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .step-title {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .step-description {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .step-details {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .step-details li {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    padding-left: var(--space-lg);
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .step-details li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent-cool);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .work-details {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-3xl);
    margin-top: var(--space-4xl);
    max-width: 900px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .detail-card {
    background-color: var(--color-base);
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent-cool);
  }

  .detail-card.highlight {
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-white);
    border-left-color: var(--color-accent-warm);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(26, 58, 82, 0.3);
    transform: scale(1.02);
  }

  .detail-card h4 {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .detail-card.highlight h4 {
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .detail-card p {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .detail-card.highlight p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .engagement-steps {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .work-details {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
